Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大男生合伙来欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是差劲  差劲透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  远坂  这跟你又没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们也来对我做同样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就和我有关系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保持平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想操控魔力必须要时刻控制好自己的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果操控有误  魔力会反噬自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过度的力量与错误的方法不仅对自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会给身边的人带来危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻牢记正确的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是远坂家的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「时刻保持从容  优雅处事」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到这种事琴音可不能忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果错在他们的话  你可得发发脾气才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛真是厉害  敢那么直接地说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢  这是很普通的事情吧  或者说理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这都是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  再多教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么才能做出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  对于现在的凛来说或许有些难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  只要凛你每天努力  总有一天能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  你可是远坂家的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小凛  这个地方可不可以教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个在教科书的23页有写
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边只是在这里计算错误了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题嘛…你看  和这个例题是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  凛好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来坐下  我按顺序教你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去禅城那边住才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦圣杯战争开始  冬木市就已不算安全之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮父亲赢得圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  不能给爸爸添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是累赘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此  这次要以比过去更齐全的准备来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包含了确保你们的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此凛和妈妈最好还是离开冬木市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  只是父亲还没有教给我足够的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己学就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.25,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启此门者为何许人也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.07,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或可为吾友朋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执吾之手  以此为誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.58,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相会于吾陋室之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝之手   是小？是大？是瘦？是硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.25,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Du,  wer die Tür geöffnet hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.07,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wird  freunde  sein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.95,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Für die Aussage nimm meine Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.58,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wir  werden  in  meinem  Zimmer  treffen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.90,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sind deine Hände, Klein? Gross? Schlank? Steif?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把书合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对凛来说  要看这本书还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上有些东西自身就带有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫魔力针
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平时不会有任何反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果附近有魔术的痕迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  你用魔力发动它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后对于刚才那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有这种反应的东西是凛还无法应付的  必须小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这个送给凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算提前送你的生日礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等圣杯战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你尝试一下更为正式的宝石魔术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于  异变开始产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是自习哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的新闻也是绑架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}最近冬木市经常发生儿童突然失踪的案件…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师他们一直在开会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第五节课不上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老师说得呆在家里不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是绑架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被绑架的都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体好像没有放进棺材里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟样子很凄惨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件的确是在冬木市发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和琴音同班的远坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在电话无人接听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在听到「嘀」的一声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…夜晚的冬木市？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和白天完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人感觉好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过这样的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是说到处都有魔力的痕迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得找到琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这么晚了还带着孩子外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险  要是被发现了肯定会被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  要好好走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩的数量变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要躲起来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  什么也做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被下了什么魔术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么  迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们正准备开派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人数还有点不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也来帮帮忙呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这种事就得人多才热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑什么跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是用那手镯  把大家给…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你还是愿意帮忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可没时间哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下估计要挨老爷骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小凛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了啊  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有这种反应的东西是凛还无法应付的  必须小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…没想到竟然会去了冬木市…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛她没事  只是睡着了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是间桐家的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肉体为巢穴  以灵魂为食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这些代价才能换来如此的魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小樱会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她变成这样之前  我一定会将她救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏砚想要的只有圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他答应我只要能得到那东西  他便会放了小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说…圣杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Servant是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的小樱来说  就连抱有希望也是一种折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请你代替那孩子祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了小樱的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  我们能回到当初一起在这个公园嬉戏的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  小凛和小樱也会重新成为姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  葵姐  你也不必再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君  你是想死吗？要和时臣同归于尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮礼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着远坂时臣的夫人和千金不管  真的妥当么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续监视Berserker的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是小事  但我也确实能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要说这样就能独当一面吧  我却又半途就晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我还不够成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这也只是现在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有足够的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  我会以远坂的魔术师这个身份开始战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这随时可能到来的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要勤学苦练  谨记父亲的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时只需要将自己所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力又优雅地完成就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有欲望的王者连装饰品都不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保护弱者的话  又有什么意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会有什么损失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是固有结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王要亲手杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想要征服世…哇！


